        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer784529074" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17740916801558782863">I would not exchange the sorrows of my heart for the joys of the multitude. And I would not have the tears that sadness makes to flow from my every part turn into laughter. I would that my life remain a tear and a smile.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


